Jack Lab - ADNI GO/2 MRI QC: 2015-12-08

Source: R/data.R
MAYOADIRL_MRI_IMAGEQC.Rd

Jack Lab - ADNI GO/2 MRI QC: 2015-12-08 data. More information is available at https://adni.loni.usc.edu/data-samples/adni-data/

Usage

data(MAYOADIRL_MRI_IMAGEQC)

Format

A data frame with 33432 observations and 41 variables.

Source

https://adni.loni.usc.edu/data-samples/adni-data/

Details

  • ORIGPROT character Original study protocol , with options: ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2

  • RID numeric Participant roster ID Range value: 21, ..., 5296

  • loni_study numeric Range value: 27356, ..., 80571

  • loni_series character

  • loni_image character

  • series_date numeric Range value: 20100617, ..., 20151028

  • series_time numeric Range value: 0, ..., 225157.18

  • series_number numeric Range value: 1, ..., 8101

  • series_description character

  • series_type character , with options: T1, AFL, T2st, ASL, fMRI, B0map, T2FSE, HighResHippo, DTI

  • software_version character

  • field_strength numeric Range value: 1.5, ..., 3

  • coil character

  • series_quality numeric Range value: -1, ..., 4

  • series_selected numeric Range value: 0, ..., 1

  • series_comments character

  • series_coverage_occipital numeric Range value: 1, ..., 1

  • series_coverage_vermis numeric Range value: 1, ..., 1

  • series_coverage_cerebellum numeric Range value: 1, ..., 1

  • series_coverage_superior numeric Range value: 1, ..., 1

  • series_coverage_temporal numeric Range value: 1, ..., 1

  • series_coverage_other logical Boolean value: TRUE/ FALSE

  • T1_ACCELERATED numeric T1 Accelerated Range value: -1, ..., 1

  • fMRI_phase numeric Range value: 0, ..., 1

  • fMRI_pencil numeric Range value: 0, ..., 1

  • fMRI_venetian numeric Range value: 0, ..., 1

  • fMRI_DMN numeric Range value: 0, ..., 1

  • fMRI_yaw numeric Range value: 0.046934, ..., 4.1313

  • fMRI_roll numeric Range value: 0.05287, ..., 8.99299

  • fMRI_pitch numeric Range value: 0.08206, ..., 6.538

  • fMRI_mmz numeric Range value: 0.06255, ..., 6.1477

  • fMRI_mmy numeric Range value: 0.05614, ..., 5.77198

  • fMRI_mmx numeric Range value: 0.04264, ..., 5.1653

  • fMRI_motion_display numeric Range value: 0, ..., 1

  • fMRI_temporal_slice_order character

  • fMRI_mean_snr numeric Range value: 1, ..., 160.746

  • fMRI_phase_direction character , with options: PA, AP, Indeterminate, NoEval

  • study_medical_abnormalities numeric Range value: 0, ..., 1

  • study_overallpass numeric Range value: -1, ..., 1

  • study_comments character

  • update_stamp POSIXct POSIXct: YYY-MM-DD
